.Dd June 03, 2026
.Dt JBUSI2C 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm jbusi2c
.Nd Sun Fire JBus I2C controller
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "jbusi2c* at mainbus0"
.Cd "iic* at jbusi2c?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the JBus I2C controller on the Sun Fire chips.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr iic 4 ,
.Xr intro 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Nx 9.0 .
.Sh AUTHORS
The
.Nm
driver was written by
.An Michael Lorenz Aq Mt macallan@netbsd.org .
